author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Pzena Investment Management Announces Jan 31, 2018 Assets Under Management
text:
February 7, 2018 / 11:18 PM / in 26 minutes BRIEF-Pzena Investment Management Announces Jan 31, 2018 Assets Under Management Reuters Staff 
Feb 7 (Reuters) - Pzena Investment Management Inc: 
* PZENA INVESTMENT MANAGEMENT, INC. ANNOUNCES JANUARY 31, 2018 ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT 
* PZENA INVESTMENT MANAGEMENT INC - ‍​TOTAL AUM $ 40.5 BILLION AS OF JANUARY 31, 2018 VERSUS $38.5 BILLION AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2017 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
